inlineContent.text: The Airwallex iOS SDK is a framework for integrating easy, fast and secure payments inside your app with Airwallex. It provides simple functions to send sensitive credit card data directly to Airwallex, it also provides a powerful, customizable interface for collecting user payment details. Follow
for steps of installation and integration.
